'''拉凱雅·威尔逊 '''（{{lang-en|Raykeea Wilson}}；{{bd|1992年|7月10日}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/aug/26/angel-haze-new-york-rapper|title=Angel Haze: 'Right now, no one can beat me'|last=Hoby|first=Hermione|date=2012-09-01|newspaper=The Guardian|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|access-date=2016-02-23|archive-date=2013-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130223120342/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/aug/26/angel-haze-new-york-rapper|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/10349936/Interview-Angel-Haze-the-rapper-fighting-rape-culture.html|title=Interview: Angel Haze, the rapper fighting rape culture|website=Telegraph.co.uk|access-date=2016-02-23|archive-date=2018-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614023948/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/10349936/Interview-Angel-Haze-the-rapper-fighting-rape-culture.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>），更为人所知的是她的艺名'''安吉尔·黑斯'''（Angel Haze），是一名美国的[[饶舌|饶舌]][[歌手|歌手]]。在2012年，黑斯在互联网上发行了一张单曲《Reservation》之后与{{le|環球共和國唱片|Universal_Republic_Records}}签下合约，之后又转移到了{{le|共和國唱片|Republic Records}}旗下。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/480478/angel-haze-talks-universal-republic-deal-debut-album-azealia-banks|title=Angel Haze Talks Universal Republic Deal, Debut Album, & Azealia Banks Collabo|website=Billboard|access-date=2016-04-18|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930185355/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/480478/angel-haze-talks-universal-republic-deal-debut-album-azealia-banks|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2013年12月31日，她发行了首张专辑《[[黑金|黑金]]》，里面包含了单曲《Echelon (It's My Way)》和 《[[战吼|战吼]]》。黑斯发行了许多混音歌曲，包括最近的《Back to the Woods》（2015）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/back-to-the-woods/angel-haze|title=Reviews for Back To The Woods by Angel Haze - Metacritic|work=Metacritic|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206001926/https://www.metacritic.com/music/back-to-the-woods/angel-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早期生活 ==
拉安·萝丝·威尔逊1992年7月10日出生在[[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[底特律|底特律]]一个军人家庭。她有非洲和美洲土著血统，她也自学了[[切罗基语|切罗基语]]。<ref name="macphersonguardian2013">{{Cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2013/jan/31/rapper-angel-haze-religion-rape-survival|title=Rapper Angel Haze on religion, rape, and survival|last=Macpherson|first=Alex|date=January 31, 2013|work=The Guardian|accessdate=June 13, 2013|location=London|archive-date=2013-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130717083027/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2013/jan/31/rapper-angel-haze-religion-rape-survival|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在[[使徒信心會|使徒信心会]]中成长但不再信教。在《卫报》的一次访谈中，她说到：“我们都生活在同一个社区里，相互之间只有10分钟的距离。你不会被允许和超过这个范围之外的人说话，你不被允许佩戴首饰，听音乐，吃某些食物，与他人约会……基本上你不会被允许干每一件事。”<ref name="macphersonguardian2013"/>然而，她16岁时因为母亲遭受到了一个牧师的威胁而举家搬迁到纽约[[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]。她便开始融入到[[世俗音樂|世俗音乐]]的世界。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2013/06/02/new-music-angel-haze-no-bueno/#more-159329|title=New Music: Angel Haze – ‘No Bueno’|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=|publisher=Rap-Up.com|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811070210/https://www.rap-up.com/2013/06/02/new-music-angel-haze-no-bueno/#more-159329|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，Haze借用[[阿姆|阿姆]]的song of the same name的Classick混音节奏演唱了歌曲《Cleaning Out My Closet》（清空我的衣柜）来讲述了自己童年时被性侵犯的经历。<ref name=":0"/>

== 音乐事业 ==
[[File:Angel_Haze_live_at_Øyafestivalen_2013.jpg|左]]
从2009年到2012年，黑斯在网络上发行了一系列的免费混音歌曲：''New Moon''、''Altered Ego''、''King'', 和''Voice''。2012年7月，发行了免费的混音专辑去赢得评论家的称赞，且在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]获得了88/100分。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/reservation-mixtape/angel-haze|title=Reviews for Reservation [Mixtape] by Angel Haze - Metacritic|work=Metacritic|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725225057/https://www.metacritic.com/music/reservation-mixtape/angel-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月9日，英国广播公司宣布黑斯获得了2013[[年度新声|年度新声]]的提名。<ref name="so13">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010q6bc/profiles/angelhaze|title=Sound of 2013 Profiles: Angel Haze|accessdate=2012-12-10|date=2012-12-09|publisher=BBC|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112205725/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010q6bc/profiles/angelhaze|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2013年8月28日，安吉尔发行了单曲《Echelon (It's My Way)》作为首张专辑《黑金》的主打歌。原本定在2014年3月发行的整张专辑在2013年12月18日泄露。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2013/12/18/angel-haze-says-fuck-you-to-label-leaks-her-album/#more-175427|title=Angel Haze Says ‘F**k You’ to Label, Leaks their Album|work=Rap-Up|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028201246/https://www.rap-up.com/2013/12/18/angel-haze-says-fuck-you-to-label-leaks-her-album/#more-175427|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑的发行被提前，通过小岛唱片和共和國唱片于2013年12月30日出现在公众视野。首周的销量不佳<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/dirty-gold/angel-haze|title=Reviews for Dirty Gold by Angel Haze - Metacritic|work=Metacritic|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203102519/https://www.metacritic.com/music/dirty-gold/angel-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>在英国卖出857张，在美国也只卖出不到1000张。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2014/01/angel-haze-addresses-low-record-sales/|title=Angel Haze Isn't Bothered By '''Her''' Low Record Sales - XXL|work=XXL|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201145443/https://www.xxlmag.com/news/2014/01/angel-haze-addresses-low-record-sales/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.factmag.com/2014/01/07/angel-hazes-dirty-gold-sells-857-copies-in-the-uk-hasnt-charted-in-the-us-billboard-200-chart/|title=Angel Haze's Dirty Gold sold 857 copies first week in the UK, not the Billboard 200 - FACT Magazine: Music News, New Music.|work=FACT Magazine: Music News, New Music.|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129074652/https://www.factmag.com/2014/01/07/angel-hazes-dirty-gold-sells-857-copies-in-the-uk-hasnt-charted-in-the-us-billboard-200-chart/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年9月14日，黑斯又发行了专辑《Back to the Woods》，声明这张专辑只是“成为大二学生之前想要分享的一些东西。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://consequenceofsound.net/2015/09/stream-angel-hazes-new-project-back-to-the-woods/|title=Stream: Angel Haze's new project Back to the Woods|accessdate=2016-01-08|publisher=|language=|website=Consequence of Sound|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915015824/http://consequenceofsound.net/2015/09/stream-angel-hazes-new-project-back-to-the-woods/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
她是一个[[泛性戀|泛性恋]]与[[性別酷兒|性别酷儿]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thesource.com/2012/07/05/angelhazewhatthisup-and-comingfemalemcsayswillmakeyoulisten/|title=Angel Haze: What This Up-And-Coming Female MC Says Will Make You Listen|date=2012-07-05|last=Osorio|first=Kim|newspaper=''[[The_Source_(magazine)|The Source]]''|access-date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018231250/https://thesource.com/2012/07/05/angelhazewhatthisup-and-comingfemalemcsayswillmakeyoulisten/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她知道榜样的作用并且说：“我很高兴有一个黑人女性代表同性恋与泛性恋发声，向我一样站在聚光灯下。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.out.com/entertainment/music/2014/02/04/emancipation-angel-haze|title=EXCLUSIVE: Angel Haze on questioning her family, her sexuality & God|website=www.out.com|access-date=2016-04-18|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205145941/https://www.out.com/entertainment/music/2014/02/04/emancipation-angel-haze|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《卫报》的一次访谈中，她谈道：“爱情是没有界限的。如果你能让我感受到，让我笑——这是很难的——但之后我就可以在一起。我不介意你有一个阴道还是[[雌雄間性|雌雄同体]]。” 黑斯喜欢用[[单数they|单数they]]作为专有的性别代词，她在接受Buzzfeed的一次采访说：“当我听到人们用‘她’这个词时我就想，''他们究竟在说谁''，你懂吗？……我对自己抱有这种想法已经有很久了。”<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/shannonkeating/the-evolution-of-angel-haze#.bcWn4ONAX|title=The Evolution Of Angel Haze|website=BuzzFeed|access-date=2016-04-18|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215102209/https://www.buzzfeed.com/shannonkeating/the-evolution-of-angel-haze#.bcWn4ONAX|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年，黑斯暗示了自己与[[艾尔兰·鲍德温|艾尔兰·鲍德温]]的恋爱关系。鲍德温在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上发布了自己与黑斯的照片，黑斯随后转发照片下说明道：“是啊今天是国际女友日……所以当然。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://instagram.com/p/rLqzvBEoHa/|title=yeah it's national girlfriend day... so of course|accessdate=April 28, 2015|last=Baldwin|first=Ireland|publisher=[[Instagram|Instagram]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429050905/https://instagram.com/p/rLqzvBEoHa/|archivedate=2015年4月29日}}</ref>黑斯认识到这段跨种族的同性爱情的重要性，提到美国媒体喜欢回避谈论她们的感情。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/angel-haze-on-ireland-baldwin-romance-an-interracial-gay-couple-i-mean-thats-just-weird-for-america-right-now-9566164.html|title=Angel Haze on Ireland Baldwin: 'An interracial gay couple, I mean that’s just weird for America right now'|last=Alexander|first=Ella|date=2014-06-27|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|deadurl=no|location=UK|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409051751/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/angel-haze-on-ireland-baldwin-romance-an-interracial-gay-couple-i-mean-thats-just-weird-for-america-right-now-9566164.html|archivedate=2015-04-09|accessdate=2016-07-01}}</ref>

